<HL>
   Bond Corp. Holders
   Approve One Part
   Of Restructuring
   ----
   By Barbara Toman
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/10/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A7A
</SO>
